[NEW] REVOSA Sick Sad World Open Hoodie

Author: @cmdr_nova@mkultra.monster

Published: 21 Oct 2015


It’s a sick sad world! Especially when you’re wearing this hoodie! Bringing back the 90s one piece of clothing at a time.

As with the other hoodie, this one comes in five sizes and includes two alphas for different sizes.

If you have any issues with fitting please contact me ASAPple.

Hoodie is available on the marketplace and at my store inworld. A demo for the hoodie is currently in the works and will be available soon.
